{"tid":2279732,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"莊韻澄閃婚！未婚夫被迅速起底失業兼破產","createTime":"2020-11-10T03:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T14:29:36.000Z","uid":235152,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"766ef09603e1899c8c093bf5612faad8b7c15bfe","tid":2279732,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T03:47:22.000Z","msg":"現年39歲的藝人兼模特兒莊韻澄（Xenia、前名莊端兒）突然宣布與小5歲的呂成忠（Joe）撻著，更即將在本周四（12/11）閃婚。而消息一出，男方則旋即被網民「起底」。而在較早前，更有香港傳媒報道，其未婚夫Joe不但負債累累，還已經申請破產！曾被收數公司追債上門。<br />\n<br />\n根據消息人士透露，Joe從事保險時欠債200多萬，於2018年尾破產，之後改名做呂雨洋。近日，Xenia終承認其實早知對方破產一事，原來在拍拖後Joe已向她交代一切，又承認主要是生意上有事令他破產。<br />\n<br />\n莊韻澄原名莊端兒，主要工作為香港女主持、模特兒及演員。而早在2013-15年度，更在《香港珠寶小姐》比賽中獲季軍及最親善小姐。"},{"pid":"ac864d3951057d8c02b74f7ff1ca149d18c67f45","tid":2279732,"uid":38518,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T03:51:17.000Z","msg":"雷雨揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951b48d48f422486d242b2534294e9d7ba5c077e","tid":2279732,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"又話it男 點解變左保險佬"},{"pid":"fd844c7c4a511b0f70f2e7f497e917467ea74f3e","tid":2279732,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"951b48d48f422486d242b2534294e9d7ba5c077e","tid":2279732,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"又話it男 點解變左保險佬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T03:59:10.000Z","msg":"以前做保險現在做it"},{"pid":"9629e7b7553e879778c146bc157fbbe25b8b1a49","tid":2279732,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"條女勁撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大波長腳<im